profile:
Rapid Stor is a FULL SERVICE moving and storage company that provides reliable movers at affordable rates. 
Our storage unit sizes vary and are temperature-controlled, clean, safe and secure. We offer rates that are all-inclusive and designed with your moving requirements in mind. 

Our all-inclusive rates at a glance:
Moving- 1 professional mover and a van/small truck  only for $89.99/hourly
               2 professional movers with truck for $139.99/hourly 
               3 professional movers with truck $189.99/hourly 
               4 professional movers $234.98/hourly (The more movers you require, saves you TIME and MONEY)

Includes: Furniture wrapping, basic moving supplies/equipment, travel expenses, loading/unloading
*Please note, there is a 3-hour minimum for our moves*

Located in Mississauga, we extend our moving and storage solutions to the entire GTA and will gladly assist with any type of desired move, whether it be residential or commercial. 

Carefully screened, trained, and highly qualified on all basis, our movers naturally provide a memorable and unique customer experience.  
We are fully licensed and insured for your comfort and assurance. We welcome all local and long distance moves- provincial wide and storage pickups. 
 
Take advantage of our storage student special 60% off smaller units for the first month and save a bunch! Also 1 month free for 1 year storage contracts for our residential and commercial clients!

Tel: 877-696-6831

profile:
Vaultra Storage is a 100% Canadian owned and operated. The company is a one-stop storage solution, featuring self storage, pick up and delivery service, LAUFT coworking spaces and rental moving boxes. Each facility offers simple, seamless and secure storage solutions for all. Whether looking to store for business or personal use, Vaultra’s team will find the services that fit their customers best.

Vaultra self storage facilities offer convenient and secure locations, with units that range from traditional drive-up, indoor, heated, climate controlled to outdoor vehicle storage. Visit vaultrastorage.ca/self-storage to find a location nearby!

The pick up and delivery service, Vaultra Door to Door, is available throughout the GTA. It's simple: Vaultra movers pick up items and store them at a Vaultra facility. When the items are needed again, Vaultra Door to Door returns them! To see service areas, as well as the Door to Door storage plans available, visit d2d.vaultra.ca.

LAUFT coworking spaces are featured in Vaultra Storage's Toronto Castlefield and Ajax locations. Their state of the art facilities are perfect for business owners and/or entrepreneurs who want a space to work, while having their inventory right around the corner. Book a coworking space at lauft.work!

The rental moving box service, Vaultra CityBoxes, offers 27” x 17” x 12” bins that are stackable and reusable. First Vaultra CityBoxes delivers the bins. Then, clients pack, move and unpack. Afterwards, they pick up the bins! To see the service area and rent moving boxes, visit vaultrastorage.ca/bin-rental.

profile:
Everyone’s needs and circumstances for downsizing, Estate Clearing and Moving are different; Alivio Solution understands that the process can be overwhelming, requiring patience and flexibility. We seek to take on the administrative burden of transitioning your home, or that of a loved one, from lived-in to sale or rent-ready so that you can focus on other aspects of your life transition. Alleviating your stress while saving you time, we look after all the details from decluttering to packing, moving, resettling, and more. Servicing Toronto and surrounding areas clients find peace of mind with Alivio.

Services include:

--> Downsizing | Decluttering | Estate Clearing
  - Auction set up
  - Donation
  - Disposal
  - Cleaning
  - Inheritance Distribution
--> Full Move Management | Packing | Downsize Moving | Unpacking | New Home Set Up
--> Staging
And more!
